50 - Pow(x, n)
Problem Statement

Implement pow(x, n), which calculates x raised to the power n (xⁿ).

Approach: Binary Exponentiation (Fast Power)

Instead of multiplying x by itself n times, we repeatedly divide the exponent by 2 and use recursion to compute smaller powers.

